<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Scold2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Scold,</orth> vb. intr. to wrangle, to brawl, to be clamorous: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.240" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 240</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 249</bibl> <cit><quote>(s. with her).</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.177" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 177</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 100</bibl> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 100</bibl> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.5.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 5, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 6, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.156" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 156</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s against the quality of flesh).</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 5</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>(the --ing winds).</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 1.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 1, 32</bibl></cit>. With an accus. denoting the effect: <cit><quote>I will have more, or s. it out of him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 175</bibl></cit>.
